{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Welcome to Doodle Factory!</h2>The perfect playground for budding factory builders! Dive into the fun with easy-going board designs that won't overwhelm. Upgrade at your own pace for a stress-free, creative adventure in factory bliss!<br><br>At Doodle Factory, we get it, factory building games can be intimidating. But fear not! We've crafted an experience just for you, with easy-going board designs that make the whole process a breeze. No need for a PhD in engineering here! Dive in, have fun, and build your dream factory without breaking a sweat. We're all about making the journey as enjoyable as the destination.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825870/extras/Board_Generate.gif?t=1727599821\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Casual Factory Building</strong>: Dive into a laid-back factory-building experience designed for players of all skill levels.<br></li><li> <strong>Dynamic Board Management</strong>: Manage multiple boards to handle your factory. Iterate your boards to improve your strategy and unlock more upgrades a long the way.<br></li><li> <strong>Stress-Free Gameplay</strong>:  Doodle Factory keeps it simple, making the journey as enjoyable as the destination.<br></li><li> <strong>Accessible for Newbies</strong>: A perfect entry point for newcomers to the factory-building genre, providing a welcoming and enjoyable experience.<br></li><li> <strong>Incremental Upgrades</strong>: Boost the efficiency of your machines and fine-tune your board generation capabilities.<br></li><li> <strong>Expert's Haven</strong>: Doodle Factory welcomes experts to showcase their mastery in intricate machine placement.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Store 1000 Common Tier 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2825870/bad0dd5ab033e7171a940938f01dd5dfdbdf5a6c.jpg"},{"name":